# Project Structure Conventions

## Monorepo Organization
- /apps: Application code
  - /api: Backend NestJS application
  - /web: Frontend React application
- /packages: Shared libraries
  - /ui: Shared UI components
  - /utils: Shared utilities

## Import Conventions
- Use @repo/* aliases for internal packages
- Use relative imports within apps
- Avoid circular dependencies
- Export public API from index files

## TypeScript Configuration
- Extend base configs from @repo/typescript-config
- Use strict mode
- Enable modern module resolution
- Share types via workspace packages

## Package Management
- Use workspace dependencies
- Define clear package boundaries
- Share devDependencies at root
- Version lock critical dependencies